title: Spork Video Mixtape #1 (1080p x264) - SPORKPRODUCTIONS
description:
Spork Video Mixtape #1: A Mental Portrait

Edited and Lovingly Assembled over 72 Feverish Hours by
Spork Productions
August 10, 2015
"Keep Circulating the Tapes!"
(PS: I used The 13 GB source file for this took 18 hours to render using my Core 2 Duo E8600 3.33 ghz desktop with 4 GB RAM. I processed it in Handbrake using slow mode to compress it to its' current size, and it plays perfectly in the free Media Player Classic (MPC) with the torrentable CoreAVC Professional Codec installed. Both are available online, so if VLC gets hung up on 1080p video for you, that's the best fix I've found.)
